==English==

===Etymology===
From the sound of their call, a beautiful liquid gurgle rising and falling like water pouring from a bottle.

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# (South Africa) Any of the [[coucal]] species ''Centropus supercilliosus, C. cupreicadus or C. senegalensis.''

====Usage note====
The common name is used throughout the birds' ranges which extend through Africa.